pan><br />\n<br />\n望吓都要打，黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「𡃁仔望乜撚嘢啊？！」嘅心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf946396aa3412db8f2a855db21e463d7911e20b","tid":464942,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}